    [21530] = {21530, "Norigorn", [[ A mysterious construct of antiquity, a living mountain of stone shaped by a strange, inexplicable logic - some of the stones look as though no hand ever touched them, while others look like materials masterfully worked by a stonemason for a fortress. Norigorn's origin is unknown, and modern mage-researchers argue themselves hoarse over the principles of magic on which this guardian operates. On one thing, however, absolutely everyone agrees - Norigorn more than fulfills its purpose and can easily overpower even exceedingly powerful lone adventurers who covet its treasures. ]], 557969, 0, 0, 11672, 21537, 21531, 0, 1, 0, 2, 2, -1, 70010},
